        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Police Officers Protecting Children Act</b></p> <p>This bill specifies that certain active and retired law enforcement officers who are authorized to carry concealed firearms are not subject to the federal prohibition on possessing (or discharging) a firearm in a school zone.</p>]]>
        </text>
